            "title": "Aurora Mobile sets US$10M stock buyback plan",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Aurora Mobile (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/JG\" title=\"Aurora Mobile Limited\">JG</a></span>) board has approved a share repurchase program to buy back up to US$10 million worth of ordinary shares (including in the form of American depositary shares) until December 31, 2026.</li>\n<li>The company expects to fund the repurchases out of its existing cash balance.</li>\n<li>Source: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20305612-aurora-mobile-announces-up-to-us-10-million-share-repurchase-program\">Press Release</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>",
