            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Sapiens <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20305601-sapiens-reports-third-quarter-2025-financial-results\">press release</a>  (SPNS): Q3  Non-GAAP EPS of $0.36 <font color=\"green\"> beats by $0.01</font>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $152.3M (+11.2% Y/Y) <font color=\"green\"> beats by $4.07M</font>.</li>\n<li>Annualized recurring revenue totaled $220 million, reflecting a 26.7% year-over-year increase, of which 17.5% is organic and 9.2% contributed from the recent acquisitions. </li>\n<li>Sapiens's non-GAAP operating profit totaled $25 million in the quarter, reflecting a 16.7% operating margin.</li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>",
